              "value": "Putrid Aura (Acid and Poison Forms Only)"
            },
            "trait_description": {
              "value": "A creature that starts its turn within 5 feet of the animated breath must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned until the start of its next turn. A creature that touches the animated breath or hits it with a melee attack takes 3 (1d6) acid damage."
